Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix:=20=F0=9F=90=9Braise=20minimum=20peer=20req?=
 =?UTF-8?q?uest=5Ftimeout=20to=2030s=20to=20avoid=20snubbing=20fast=20loca?=
 =?UTF-8?q?lhost=20peers?=
